Package: bsvars
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Estimation of Structural Vector Autoregressive Models
Version: 0.0.2.9000
Date: 2022-08-29
Author: person("Tomasz", "Woźniak", , "wozniak.tom@pm.me", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2212-2378"))
Description: This package provides efficient algorithms for Bayesian estimation of Structural Vector Autoregressive (SVAR) models via Markov chain Monte Carlo methods. A wide range of SVAR models is considered, including homo- and heteroskedastic specifications and those with non-normal structural shocks.
License: GPL (>= 3)
